entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
entries.split_quest_alert: Coynite ships and smugglers seem to be working together. We need you to capture one of the mercenaries and return it to HQ.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Coynite Ambush
entries.title_d: A group of mercenaries arrived too late to stop you from getting the shuttle to safety. Destroy these mercenaries.
